Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:03:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where they faced the New Fish-Man Pirates  \Nwho were looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and instigated an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea Kings stopped the Noah from \Nfalling onto the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot stop Luffy-sama's bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's F.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have as much as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:15.77,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Secret Revealed! The Truth \Nabout the Ancient Weapon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The royal family came to a decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We are free!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Hordy! Look at yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna be a slave forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hats! I owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! That's a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I-I'm gonna become king...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally I can set sail for the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about releasing \NHordy's human slaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their anger against Hordy could \Nturn towards all Fish-Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island has always been a place \Nfor pirates to travel and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since they meant no harm to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no reason to hold them here-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for the rest of the \NNew Fish-Man Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't cut my head off!\N--P-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't even know that \NHordy killed the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all nuts, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's right!\N--It's Hordy's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I order you all to live on this main island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you telling us \Nto live law-abiding lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds better than working under Hordy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, King-sama! We \Ndon't want them among us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let our kids walk the streets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I meant they need \Nto do their time and work
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the supervision of my army-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you all jobs to use \Nup your overflowing energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today on, the Fish-Man District
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be sealed off since it \Nis out of our control-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dark side of the Fish-Men was exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with the real killer of Queen Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate - Hordy Jones attempted \Nto take over the Fish-Man Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but his plans
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were foiled by human pirates who \Nwere just stopping by the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where is Straw Hat Luffy-jamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... He escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escaped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to leave the plaza \Nas though you were running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see? We had to fight \Nwith a lot of spectators watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stayed, they'd treat \Nus like heroes or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the thought of it makes me shudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming a hero is not a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hero is someone who will share \Nhis own sake with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanna drink it all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, that's not how you define a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you join us, Jimbei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on an adventure with us! \NTo the sea! It's gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, join us, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to have  a former Warlord with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Luffy,  you need a complete rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, I can't join you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful that you asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it'd be fun to sail \Nthe sea with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still have things that need to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my current responsibilities which
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI'm just taking a break from right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fulfill my duties \Nand am free from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I will come to see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you haven't changed your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can I take you up on your offer then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You swear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa whoa, when a man talks about \Nhis "duty," you can't press him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes Jimbei so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy thinks so highly of you! So \Nwe're all gonna wait for you, Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what are we gonna do? \NHead for the New World?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you going to leave the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't thank you properly \Nand didn't get to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's stay at the \NMermaid Cafe for a week or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be just up your alley, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanna go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A soldier of Neptune's army?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune! I caught up with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun, why did you leave? \NI wanted to thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Let's just have a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The banquet we could not have before-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A banquet?! Then I'll \Nbe right there! Banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Meat, meat! I wanna eat!\N--Boy! Then why did we leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't say no to a banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go pick up Hachi and Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fish-Man District was sealed \Noff right away by Neptune's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy, the officers of the New Fish-Man \NPirates, and Vander Decken...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were placed in the Prison Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.74,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MAIN ENTRANCE OF THE FISH-MAN ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kraken! Take him somewhere far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wadatsumi, you don't fit into \Nany of the cells in the prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We forbid you from entering \Nthis country again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:50.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CORAL HILL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's prepare these and \Ntake them to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll have a big banquet \Nwith the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they like sea monster meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take snacks and cakes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:08.39,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CANDY FACTORY TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they eat a lot. Take all we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have enough sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to have our highest quality sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the palace-jamon, \NLuffy-kun, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk later during the banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.16,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,RYUGU PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The long flounders will take \Nyou to the banquet hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whew! These rays are huge!\N--They're flukes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just said "flounders."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dark room filled with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really allowed in? I'm nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never entered the palace before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this place? What happened \Nto the meat and banquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here comes the heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's filled with soldiers down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving the Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never forget what you did for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes! Heroes! Heroes! Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop calling us \N"heroes"! I wanna eat meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! I wanna drink sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama! There is a stage \Nright in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen! Let's start \Nthe banquet with the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we present you the greatest \Ndiva of the deep sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria Napole!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Swing Jazz Orchestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a sweet voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Maria-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is rocking my soul! Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the special guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their beauty takes your breath away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mermaid Cafe Dancers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna die, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their beauty can't be captured \Nin a picture! No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm losing my strength...\N--Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Awesome!\N--Fascinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishilly! I'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes! There's no \Nhaving a banquet without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Super I've been waiting for this!\N--That's how the Ryugu Palace should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, King, will you give a toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I give a toast, I really want \Nto express my gratitude briefly-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's banquet time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know. Nobody \Nwants to hear me-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat! Sing! Drink! Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need more obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You eat a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, sisters, dance with me! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll dance.\N--I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Maybe I'll dance.\N--I'll dance, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! You have great snacks on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island's sake is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already had it once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you got caught for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about those little things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Hero-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard, I didn't think of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dying-bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't push yourself like that, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're gonna die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody cares about me-jamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hairy old man doesn't look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat-san! Don't \Nbe rude to the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin! Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, raise your glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, hairy old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to express my gratitude briefly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers-jamon! Oh, whatever-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers to you guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very good. I wonder if \Nit's because of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can tell the difference, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so pale?! It's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moonfish! Shake, shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance more, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat, drink and make some \Nnoise-mi-fa-so-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to talk \Nto me about, pirate girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I thought this was my only \Nchance to talk to you in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I will tell you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a wife named Otohime \Nwho I swore to love forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although she is dead, I am \Nnot going to cheat on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Joy Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read the Poneglyph in the Sea Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he apologizing to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a survivor of Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me \Neverything if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joy Boy was a person from \Nabove ground who lived
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the Hundred Year Void-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means more than 800 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That message was written \Nto a Mermaid Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was on this island at that time-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a letter of apology for not \Nkeeping his promise to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know the details of his promise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they say somebody will come and \Nfulfill it on behalf of Joy Boy someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the story handed \Ndown in our royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we believe the day will come
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have continued
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,looking after the Noah for generations \Njust as we promised him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the day comes, the Noah will be put
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto its true use for the first time-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard when all the battles \Ncame to an end today,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the half-destroyed Noah was \Ntaken to the Sea Forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by the Sea Kings!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Joy Boy had power to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,control Sea Kings since he \Nwas going to use the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the former Mermaid Princess was \Nthe one who had such power-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Princess Shirahoshi \Nhas that same power?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it awoke completely today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 years ago at a Sky Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read a Poneglyph indicating where \None of the ancient weapons is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pointing at this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mermaid Princess who lived \Naround the same time as Joy Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was known by a specific name, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Princess Shirahoshi has the same \Npower, she will inherit that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another name for her will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the ancient weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Poseidon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei reveals speaks about \Ntwo important matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Whitebeard's death, distribution of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,power among pirates in the \NNew World was decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by none other than one \Nof the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a fierce and epic battle \Noccurred within the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its shocking conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...becomes a big obstacle for \NLuffy as he enters the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Straw Hats Stunned! The \NNew Fleet Admiral of the Navy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.72,0:23:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
